c: 6
v: 137
t: Aur issi tarah boht say mushrikeen kay khayal mein unn kay maboodon ney unn ki aulad kay qatal kerney ko mustehsan bana rakha hai takay woh inn ko barbad keren aur takay inn kay deen ko inn per mushtaba ker den aur agar Allah ko manzoor hota to yeh aisa kaam na kertay to aap inn ko aur jo kuch ghalat baaten yeh bana rahey hain yun hi rehney dijiye